introduction:
Hi, I'm Minho Cho. 
 As you can tell, I program, travel, and write articles about my travels.
 Most of my programming projects are viewable on my Github. I'm always looking for new things to do with programming skills so please do not hesistate to contact me if you are also interested. 
 I'm trying to start a Youtube channel for the purpose of sharing memories with family and friends. 
 I also have a travel Instagram where I write about my travels around the world. My ultimate goal in doing this is publishing my own travel essay. 
 Feel free to reach out to me. I am always open for collaborations of any sort.
